{"tid":641671,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[ARPG+SLG] 《ALAZ 天翼之戰》 (1)","createTime":"2018-04-25T07:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T18:23:17.000Z","uid":31029,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dec800d02448aed89e18169a8dc3c97df3fee075","tid":641671,"uid":31029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/152949_cfaf53a74c615cfd463567961f82bd03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F152949_cfaf53a74c615cfd463567961f82bd03.png&h=946e05e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://luthiel.iwplay.com.tw/mobi-v2/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fluthiel.iwplay.com.tw%2Fmobi-v2%2Findex.html&d=mamiB8kKqeBR%2BeAuePE5xHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=fbad6725\" target=\"_blank\">https://luthiel.iwplay.com.tw/mobi-v2/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國首款華麗戰略動作手遊《ALAZ 天翼之戰》遊戲展示影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TokGGG8OZn8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTokGGG8OZn8&d=mamiB8kKqeBR%2BeAuePE5xHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2db300be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TokGGG8OZn8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/153635_a33b50407814497c0cbed6a6751cf3c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F153635_a33b50407814497c0cbed6a6751cf3c5.png&h=e71d5c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《ALAZ 天翼之戰》是一款結合『ARPG+SLG』的遊戲作品，世界觀圍繞在『天』與『魔』如何在對立中為了守護家園轉而團結對抗龍族，所以玩家在遊戲中除了能體驗到驚心動魄的動作戰鬥畫面，還能以獨創性360度3D視角方式展開要塞攻城戰，非常考驗怎麼將手中的英雄特性作最大的發揮，玩家可以化身領主，在展開難以預測的奇襲攻城以外，建築屬於自己的堅固領地，用自己的力量保衛家園！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/154003_ee66dd538e4f36aa0d5087834fa10fb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F154003_ee66dd538e4f36aa0d5087834fa10fb3.png&h=dae746f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《ALAZ 天翼之戰》還有另一個特色玩法，玩家可以透過十種職業與上百位來自天族、魔族、龍族、蛙人、獸人與白貂等不同種族英雄，量身打造領主陣容。另外，我們也和營運團隊一起規劃專屬台港澳地區的遊戲內容，像是將加強新手英雄的絕招視覺效果；將特定英雄在要塞戰、競技場中增加特殊屬性，以及專屬主城任務、大型公會戰等內容，請玩家們敬請期待！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/153800_b8bd184202e114f02165d5d80b30408c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F153800_b8bd184202e114f02165d5d80b30408c.png&h=87f8c16e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3360c8ba302e53aa0eff1c45a17419929945b38d","tid":641671,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"玩左一陣都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18db1c1e4268bb152290f28cb8e779a4650015c4","tid":641671,"uid":15154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人開公會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8426c80e33e90d5da8f3a42367105cf49ceb0e","tid":641671,"uid":124876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫ARPG+SLG?"},{"pid":"183d0e1d35bc11de39fbf21a2ead74c5a9f09dea","tid":641671,"uid":11180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"點解有時打打吓普通關卡  會有人亂入嘅？"},{"pid":"85698f28746cb7c4f1547ba4a85d3c35f5d64df9","tid":641671,"uid":31029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d8426c80e33e90d5da8f3a42367105cf49ceb0e","tid":641671,"uid":124876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫ARPG+SLG?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"鬼知咩 個網咁寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af674c1932a665291697862664fe2ff33c4c779d","tid":641671,"uid":51456,"like":1,"dislike":0,